hotel_text.important_information:
Please note construction work is going on nearby from 7:00 to 16:00 and some rooms may be affected by noise. The property apologizes for any inconvenience caused.

Guests are required to show a photo ID and credit card upon check-in. Please note that all Special Requests are subject to availability and additional charges may apply.  A damage deposit of VND 466846.53 is required on arrival. This will be collected as a cash payment. You should be reimbursed on check-out. Your deposit will be refunded in full, in cash, subject to an inspection of the property.

policies.content: You'll be charged 50% of the total price if you cancel your booking.

All children are welcome. Up to three children under 7 years stay free of charge when using existing beds.
Up to three children from 7 to 11 year are charged  VND 100000 per night when using existing beds.
There is no capacity for extra beds in the room.
The maximum number of total guests in a room is 9.
There is no capacity for cribs in the room.
Additional fees are not calculated automatically in the total cost and will have to be paid for separately during your stay.
WiFi is available in all areas and is free of charge.
Free private parking is available  on site (reservation is not needed).
Pets are not allowed.
You'll be charged a prepayment of 50% of the total price in the 7 days before arrival.
The property reserves the right to pre-authorize credit cards prior to arrival.
VND 466,846.53 Damage deposit per stay is excluded. A VAT is not applicable. A City tax is not applicable.
